003package es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.abstracttppstep;
004
005import java.util.List;
006import java.util.Map;
007
008import javax.json.Json;
009import javax.json.JsonObject;
010
011import lombok.AccessLevel;
012import lombok.Getter;
013import lombok.NonNull;
014
015/**
016 * Enumerates all the applicable JSON types for an attribute that are to be
017 * found in a Text Processing Python response.
018 *
019 * @author Alejandro González García
020 */
021public enum JsonResponseAttributeType {
022        /**
023         * A JSON array of strings.
024         */
025        STRING_ARRAY(List.of("")),
026        /**
027         * A JSON string.
028         */
029        STRING("");
030
031        @Getter(AccessLevel.PACKAGE) @NonNull
032        private final JsonObject dummyValue;
033
034        /**
035         * Instantiates a new enum constant. This method is to be invoked by the JVM
036         * only.
037         *
038         * @param value The value to put in the dummy JSON value.
039         */
040        private JsonResponseAttributeType(@NonNull final Object value) {
041                this.dummyValue = Json.createObjectBuilder(Map.of("text", value)).build();
042        }
043}
